Description: Tools that make AquaCropv7 files handling easier.In other words, some functions that can allow you to handle aquacrop v7 data really quicly. AquaCrop is a crop growth model developed by the Land and Water Division of FAO to address food security and to assess the effect of environment and management on crop production.
